# IndigenousACCESS / TribalWeather Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in values

# =============================================================================
# OPTIONAL: TestSprite E2E Testing
# =============================================================================
# Get your API key from https://testsprite.com
# TESTSPRITE_API_KEY=your_api_key_here

# =============================================================================
# NOTE: External APIs Used (No Keys Required)
# =============================================================================
# The following APIs are used and do NOT require API keys:
#
# 1. NWS Weather API (api.weather.gov)
#    - Alerts for WA, OR, ID, PZ (Pacific marine zones)
#    - 7-day forecasts via grid points
#
# 2. Environment Canada MSC Datamart (dd.weather.gc.ca)
#    - CAP alerts for BC and Alberta
#    - Radar via WMS (geo.weather.gc.ca)
#
# 3. NOAA River Gauges (api.water.noaa.gov)
#    - NWPS flood gauge data for WA, OR, ID
#
# 4. NOAA NEXRAD Radar (mesonet.agron.iastate.edu)
#    - Real-time weather radar tiles via Iowa State
#
# 5. CARTO Basemaps (basemaps.cartocdn.com)
#    - Dark Matter tile layer for map background
